data.description: Welcome to this updated 5-bedroom, 4-bath colonial home, thoughtfully designed to meet modern living needs. This spacious residence comes complete with an in-law suite, making it perfect for multi-generational families or accommodating guests. Inside, you'll find a harmonious blend of classic charm and contemporary updates with a beautiful walk in closet. The kitchen features modern appliances and a sleek design. With five bedrooms and four tastefully appointed bathrooms, there's plenty of space for everyone to enjoy and spread out. Step outside into the fenced backyard, where a lovely patio invites you to relax and soak up the serenity of your private outdoor haven. The new owner will get to enjoy updates such as a new roof (2021), hot water tank (2021), carpet + laminate (2021/2023), stamped patio (2020) and updated sewers to ensure POS compliance (2021). Additional basement space, added in 2012, offers a canvas for your imagination to run wild. Whether you envision a cozy retreat for movie nights and gaming, a home gym to break a sweat, a playroom for the kids, or even a versatile workspace, this basement provides the room you need to bring your ideas to life. With ample square footage at your disposal, this basement is ready to be transformed into the ultimate destination for relaxation, entertainment, or productivity. This is one of the biggest homes you will find in this neighborhood. Seller is offering an Old Republic home warranty along with a brand new driveway!
